title: RGP-2.2: Returning Forfeited Staking Rewards
body:
# Summary
Proposal to finalize the redistribution of forfeited staking rewards. The full proposal can be seen [here](https://gov.ribbon.finance/t/rgp2-2-returning-forfeited-staking-rewards/)

If passed, the proposal will redistribute the forfeited rewards to 730 addresses, which can be seen [here](https://github.com/ribbon-finance/data/blob/e22dbcbc5305df7cfc658ac238913cd5c6a9b00a/disperse_payouts.txt). The core team will execute this proposal by Dispersing the RBN, so no action is necessary from users. 

We are setting the expiry of this vote to 4th August Noon UTC. If passed, the core team will execute the proposal on 5th of August.
